Qc2 (15. Nf3 fxe4 16. Nh4 {1-0 (43) Postny,E (2619)-Pinal,N (2320) Baku 2016}
gxh5 17. Bxh5 Rf4) (15. hxg6 hxg6 16. exf5 {leads to similar play as in the
